WEBVTT

00:11.880 --> 00:13.510
This is the map of the park.

00:14.030 --> 00:15.890
Let me teach you how to look for it.

00:16.230 --> 00:17.770
First, we need to divide it into

00:16.430 --> 00:22.430
[1997]

00:17.800 --> 00:19.670
a 9 by 10 grid.

00:20.140 --> 00:21.800
Why is it 9 by 10?

00:22.710 --> 00:25.030
Because I always score 90 on my exams.

00:27.000 --> 00:29.000
Our current location is right here.

00:29.030 --> 00:30.190
It's a corridor.

00:30.230 --> 00:33.960
The corresponding numbers
for the corridor are 3 and 5.

00:34.150 --> 00:35.210
Do you understand?

00:37.150 --> 00:39.410
Then what numbers represent this place?

00:40.670 --> 00:43.520
The numbers for this are...

00:43.550 --> 00:44.320
3

00:44.600 --> 00:45.790
and 6.

00:46.110 --> 00:47.920
So it's 36.

00:48.280 --> 00:48.810
Correct.

00:49.030 --> 00:51.600
This is the small bridge behind us.

00:53.790 --> 00:56.350
It's also Bin's favorite hiding spot.

00:57.240 --> 00:59.110
These numbers and locations—

01:00.750 --> 01:02.010
can you memorize them?

01:04.349 --> 01:04.950
Yes.

01:05.560 --> 01:06.070
Good.

01:06.790 --> 01:08.760
Watch my hand signals later.

01:09.230 --> 01:10.630
You hit wherever I point.

01:11.430 --> 01:11.789
Okay!

01:12.789 --> 01:14.150
Seven.

01:15.400 --> 01:16.430
Six.

01:18.480 --> 01:19.560
Five.

01:20.280 --> 01:21.430
Four.

01:22.310 --> 01:23.560
Three.

01:24.200 --> 01:25.280
Two.

01:25.590 --> 01:26.400
One.

01:27.710 --> 01:28.840
Are you done hiding?

01:28.920 --> 01:30.450
I'm going to start looking!

03:04.950 --> 03:10.580
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:10.890 --> 03:13.190
[Episode 16]

03:15.560 --> 03:16.020
Well...

03:18.280 --> 03:19.680
Has something happened?

03:22.000 --> 03:23.630
It's my fault. My apologies.

03:24.310 --> 03:25.520
I originally wanted

03:25.520 --> 03:26.910
to help out.

03:27.480 --> 03:28.340
I didn't expect

03:28.960 --> 03:30.120
to break the pot

03:30.360 --> 03:31.520
and scare her.

03:36.750 --> 03:37.829
I'm really sorry.

03:38.560 --> 03:39.800
My wife is easily frightened.

03:39.800 --> 03:41.870
She gets nervous easily.

03:44.240 --> 03:45.520
You got burned, right?

03:46.400 --> 03:48.130
Let me take you to the hospital.

03:50.190 --> 03:50.840
It's fine.

03:51.800 --> 03:53.079
You just stay with your wife.

03:53.079 --> 03:54.340
We can go by ourselves.

03:55.840 --> 03:56.570
Don't worry.

03:56.890 --> 03:57.820
I'll be with her.

03:59.079 --> 03:59.560
Okay.

03:59.680 --> 04:01.800
W-Well, I'm sorry about this.

04:02.470 --> 04:04.470
If anything comes up later, just...

04:04.800 --> 04:05.730
Just contact me.

04:06.120 --> 04:06.850
Don't worry.

04:08.590 --> 04:09.790
We'll be leaving now.

04:10.030 --> 04:10.680
Okay.

04:21.950 --> 04:22.720
Take care.

04:30.510 --> 04:31.240
How are you?

04:37.680 --> 04:38.480
It's fine now.

04:39.070 --> 04:39.830
I'm here.

04:43.900 --> 04:44.900
Let me take a look.

04:53.480 --> 04:55.140
Bold enough to grab the knife?

04:55.250 --> 04:56.950
If I hadn't done that, you would have.

04:56.950 --> 04:58.270
In this kind of situation,

04:58.270 --> 04:59.470
it's better if I do it.

05:01.210 --> 05:01.870
How are you?

05:02.440 --> 05:03.170
Does it hurt?

05:04.390 --> 05:06.320
Now we've become bros in distress.

05:09.650 --> 05:12.250
Companions in adversity
have deep affection.

05:12.530 --> 05:13.530
Those are lyrics.

05:15.160 --> 05:17.220
Don't you dislike songs with lyrics?

05:21.190 --> 05:23.650
Your playlist is a bit old,
Professor Jiang.

05:23.950 --> 05:25.680
Let's go to the hospital first.

06:00.800 --> 06:01.360
Honey.

06:02.070 --> 06:02.830
I'm out.

06:04.890 --> 06:06.850
Don't worry, I'll be right back.

06:15.330 --> 06:16.950
Honey, where did you go?

06:17.270 --> 06:18.200
Fooling around?

06:20.390 --> 06:22.270
If you ever dare to touch her again,

06:22.270 --> 06:23.240
I'll kill you.

06:33.430 --> 06:34.310
You're sweating so much.

06:34.310 --> 06:35.240
Where did you go?

06:38.920 --> 06:39.920
It's too hot.

06:40.120 --> 06:41.320
Come have some water.

06:47.070 --> 06:47.600
Play it.

06:50.650 --> 06:51.580
I want to hear it.

08:28.560 --> 08:29.000
Mom.

08:30.700 --> 08:31.140
Mom!

08:32.020 --> 08:32.500
Mom!

08:33.440 --> 08:34.120
Mom!

08:47.960 --> 08:48.720
Someone is hurt.

08:48.720 --> 08:49.720
Save them, quick!

08:50.270 --> 08:50.840
Comrade,

08:51.000 --> 08:51.550
wake up.

08:51.650 --> 08:52.100
Kid!

08:52.120 --> 08:52.670
Comrade,

08:53.130 --> 08:54.190
-wake up!
-Wake up!

08:54.840 --> 08:55.570
Are you okay?

08:56.010 --> 08:57.890
It's likely a suicide by wrist-slashing.

08:57.890 --> 08:58.700
Go get a towel!

09:03.200 --> 09:04.150
Hurry up and bring the car.

09:04.150 --> 09:05.080
Don't touch her.

09:06.180 --> 09:06.660
Kid,

09:07.150 --> 09:08.350
I'm a police officer.

09:08.790 --> 09:10.150
I'm saving your mom.

09:11.150 --> 09:12.030
Don't worry.

09:20.390 --> 09:21.320
Don't be afraid.

11:51.070 --> 11:51.710
How is it?

11:53.720 --> 11:55.380
Foreigners know their stuff.

11:55.630 --> 11:56.960
They only want the best.

12:04.150 --> 12:05.030
Give them this.

12:06.120 --> 12:07.200
It's perfect.

12:23.840 --> 12:24.840
Young Master Wen,

12:25.390 --> 12:27.480
what do you plan for Jiang Cheng to do?

12:30.440 --> 12:31.440
Young Master Wen?

12:44.240 --> 12:45.040
What's wrong?

12:48.790 --> 12:49.670
Is he upset?

12:51.790 --> 12:53.870
People are born different.

12:54.080 --> 12:57.010
Wen Lang has been playing the piano
since he was a kid.

13:03.440 --> 13:05.150
It's just a piano.

13:07.270 --> 13:08.670
It's not that bad.

13:17.870 --> 13:18.750
Let me tell you.

13:19.390 --> 13:20.840
This piano is like a person.

13:20.840 --> 13:22.900
If you care about it, it's something.

13:23.280 --> 13:24.230
If you don't,

13:24.270 --> 13:26.080
it's nothing!

13:27.150 --> 13:27.720
Right?

13:41.960 --> 13:43.160
What did you just say?

13:45.240 --> 13:46.390
I said...

13:46.790 --> 13:48.080
I'm just asking.

13:49.360 --> 13:51.930
Since you let Jiang Cheng
into the production area,

13:51.930 --> 13:54.190
are you planning for him to do something?

14:11.120 --> 14:12.380
When he's seen enough,

14:14.720 --> 14:15.480
bring him up.

14:42.230 --> 14:43.090
How do you feel?

14:46.150 --> 14:47.280
I don't understand.

14:47.510 --> 14:49.310
Boss He sent you to get the goods.

14:50.000 --> 14:51.400
The goods are right here.

14:53.120 --> 14:56.380
I just didn't expect you to produce
and sell it yourselves.

15:01.710 --> 15:03.070
The finest ingredients

15:05.510 --> 15:07.840
often require only the simplest cooking.

15:08.150 --> 15:09.000
Is it simple?

15:09.840 --> 15:11.440
The hard part is management.

15:13.580 --> 15:14.310
Jiang Cheng.

15:16.390 --> 15:17.850
I think you've seen it too.

15:18.510 --> 15:19.790
Qi is getting old.

15:20.800 --> 15:22.630
Qiu Ye needs to stay by my side.

15:23.510 --> 15:24.480
Mr. He

15:25.000 --> 15:26.860
has his own business to attend to.

15:27.150 --> 15:29.080
So I am in urgent need of talent now.

15:30.000 --> 15:31.630
I need the right people

15:32.200 --> 15:33.840
in the right positions.

15:34.670 --> 15:36.530
Just tell me what you need me to do.

15:37.320 --> 15:38.510
I want you to stay

15:39.270 --> 15:40.730
and help me move the goods.

15:40.870 --> 15:41.530
How's that?

15:48.630 --> 15:49.200
Sure.

15:50.370 --> 15:51.000
I have

15:51.150 --> 15:53.010
nowhere else to go anyway.

16:06.240 --> 16:06.750
What?

16:08.030 --> 16:08.840
Are you upset?

16:09.970 --> 16:11.300
I'm just stating facts.

16:11.900 --> 16:13.140
I must be on the police's

16:13.140 --> 16:14.600
wanted list by now anyway.

16:14.600 --> 16:16.510
I can't survive without you.

16:17.320 --> 16:19.180
Good thing there's a sanctuary like this.

16:19.180 --> 16:21.580
Otherwise, I wouldn't even know how I died.

16:27.130 --> 16:28.130
You feel wronged?

16:28.240 --> 16:30.240
What's there to feel wronged about?

16:30.750 --> 16:32.010
I'm here too, aren't I?

16:32.150 --> 16:33.680
Look, he feels wronged too.

16:38.910 --> 16:40.240
How do we move the goods?

16:40.320 --> 16:41.050
It's simple.

16:41.730 --> 16:44.030
Give them whatever they want,
as much as they want.

16:44.030 --> 16:45.080
Qiu Ye told me

16:45.360 --> 16:46.740
you know this route well.

16:46.740 --> 16:49.150
So I'm 100% confident leaving it to you.

16:51.600 --> 16:52.530
Who is the buyer?

16:57.000 --> 16:58.030
When the time comes, the buyer will

16:58.030 --> 16:59.830
contact you through this phone.

17:02.380 --> 17:04.780
I will also contact you
through this phone.

17:06.109 --> 17:08.440
There is a bank card linked to this phone.

17:09.310 --> 17:10.400
Use it freely.

17:10.790 --> 17:11.720
Freely?

17:11.750 --> 17:13.069
Freely.

17:14.510 --> 17:16.510
That sounds like a pretty good deal.

17:20.200 --> 17:20.849
Then,

17:22.270 --> 17:23.000
Jiang Cheng,

17:24.440 --> 17:25.700
I'll take that as a yes.

17:28.569 --> 17:29.740
From now on,

17:30.400 --> 17:31.960
you are Old Scorpion.

17:33.350 --> 17:34.400
What do you mean?

17:36.000 --> 17:37.880
Old Scorpion is just a title.

17:38.920 --> 17:40.270
It can be a symbol.

17:41.720 --> 17:43.050
Or it can be a trademark.

17:43.440 --> 17:44.110
Or

17:44.400 --> 17:46.130
when you go to pick up a package,

17:46.510 --> 17:47.960
it can be your pseudonym.

17:48.640 --> 17:49.770
Whoever needs to be,

17:50.920 --> 17:51.880
is him.

17:52.980 --> 17:54.110
That sounds casual.

17:54.510 --> 17:55.400
The buyer

17:56.550 --> 17:59.830
only moves goods through Old Scorpion.

18:00.270 --> 18:01.600
Whoever moves the goods

18:02.270 --> 18:03.510
is Old Scorpion.

18:05.550 --> 18:06.070
Wait.

18:06.770 --> 18:08.970
Can I understand it as,

18:09.040 --> 18:10.890
if the deal succeeds,
Old Scorpion takes the money.

18:10.890 --> 18:12.270
If the deal fails...

18:14.640 --> 18:15.920
You cannot fail.

18:16.270 --> 18:17.670
You have no right to fail.

18:19.240 --> 18:20.700
Killing a police officer.

18:21.030 --> 18:21.830
Making drugs.

18:23.400 --> 18:24.750
Drug trafficking.

18:26.510 --> 18:27.830
If you get caught...

18:28.000 --> 18:28.730
Understood.

18:29.590 --> 18:30.720
If I get caught,

18:31.310 --> 18:32.830
I'll be your scapegoat.

18:33.140 --> 18:34.230
No, no!

18:35.510 --> 18:36.770
You are one of my lives.

18:38.030 --> 18:40.070
You are a part of my life.

18:40.350 --> 18:41.720
If you die,

18:44.720 --> 18:46.380
that would be my biggest loss.

18:50.680 --> 18:51.440
Really.

18:54.920 --> 18:56.790
I'm really curious about something.

18:56.790 --> 18:58.350
Was Qi Yan, who died 5 years ago,

18:58.350 --> 19:00.510
also one of your lives?

19:08.920 --> 19:10.240
Why mention him?

19:10.590 --> 19:11.640
I'm just curious.

19:21.790 --> 19:24.160
Curiosity isn't always a good thing.

19:25.510 --> 19:26.720
Let me put it this way.

19:27.600 --> 19:29.000
You and he are different.

19:29.920 --> 19:32.320
He was chosen by fate.
You were chosen by me.

19:33.480 --> 19:34.350
Chosen by fate?

19:35.750 --> 19:36.880
Which ranks higher?

19:44.590 --> 19:45.640
You.

20:01.790 --> 20:03.350
Since I am already Old Scorpion,

20:03.350 --> 20:04.880
can I negotiate some terms?

20:05.030 --> 20:05.510
Speak.

20:06.160 --> 20:08.400
I don't want to fight
unprepared battles anymore,

20:08.400 --> 20:09.750
nor do I want to be treated like a fool

20:09.750 --> 20:11.240
and played around with anymore.

20:11.240 --> 20:11.880
Go on.

20:12.150 --> 20:13.980
I want to contact the buyer
to move a batch of goods first.

20:13.980 --> 20:15.000
It can be a smaller amount—

20:15.000 --> 20:16.230
just to test the waters.

20:16.230 --> 20:17.640
I will decide the time and place.

20:17.640 --> 20:20.100
Once that is done,
we can talk about the rest.

20:20.480 --> 20:21.160
Fine.

20:21.960 --> 20:23.200
But things are tense lately.

20:23.200 --> 20:24.680
I need to send a few guys to follow you.

20:24.680 --> 20:25.740
No problem, right?

20:25.880 --> 20:26.540
No problem.

20:26.680 --> 20:27.510
Of course not.

20:28.400 --> 20:29.640
Dahua has to follow me.

20:29.640 --> 20:30.270
Sure.

20:30.550 --> 20:31.480
You have my word.

20:31.920 --> 20:32.590
Also,

20:32.640 --> 20:34.570
I can't live without the internet.

20:34.830 --> 20:37.200
Playing cards, gaming, eating hot pot—

20:37.400 --> 20:39.260
you can satisfy all these, right?

20:39.720 --> 20:40.680
Cheng,

20:41.070 --> 20:42.870
do you think you are on vacation?

20:43.270 --> 20:43.920
Boss,

20:44.270 --> 20:46.670
life is short,
we must enjoy it while we can.

21:03.860 --> 21:05.320
Enjoy it while we can, huh?

21:05.640 --> 21:06.720
Fine, I'll agree to that.

21:06.720 --> 21:07.400
I will arrange

21:07.400 --> 21:09.130
a relatively nice room for you.

21:09.310 --> 21:10.400
But as you can see,

21:10.810 --> 21:13.210
every room here has surveillance cameras.

21:13.590 --> 21:15.250
Including when you're eating

21:15.590 --> 21:16.550
and sleeping.

21:17.920 --> 21:19.350
You'll have to be watched

21:20.400 --> 21:21.550
24 hours a day.

21:21.920 --> 21:23.440
There are no blind spots.

21:23.640 --> 21:24.900
Are you okay with that?

21:25.280 --> 21:26.720
Whether I can accept it or not,

21:26.720 --> 21:28.250
didn't you guys just see it?

21:29.240 --> 21:30.750
If I am not wrong,

21:30.750 --> 21:32.350
this phone should have something like

21:32.350 --> 21:35.150
location tracking
and voice monitoring systems,

21:35.270 --> 21:35.680
right?

21:37.200 --> 21:38.160
Interesting.

21:40.200 --> 21:41.660
You're very interesting.

21:50.270 --> 21:51.880
If I had known this,

21:53.070 --> 21:54.750
I should have gone with you.

21:55.310 --> 21:58.040
If you went,
there would just be one more bandage.

21:58.180 --> 21:59.710
I was a detective.

22:01.000 --> 22:01.680
Prof.

22:02.110 --> 22:03.240
I have reason to believe

22:03.240 --> 22:04.700
that Qi Yan's twin brother

22:04.920 --> 22:06.180
lived until 5 years ago

22:06.480 --> 22:07.920
and didn't die young.

22:08.590 --> 22:10.590
It's just that we didn't ask further

22:10.680 --> 22:11.920
regarding the twins.

22:15.400 --> 22:17.860
There probably won't be more breakthroughs

22:17.920 --> 22:19.320
through Qi Zhen anymore.

22:20.640 --> 22:22.750
These are the people
I'm afraid of encountering—

22:22.750 --> 22:23.740
they would rather commit suicide

22:23.740 --> 22:25.450
than say another word.

22:27.030 --> 22:27.830
But Qi Yan is no longer

22:27.830 --> 22:29.160
a blurry figure.

22:30.200 --> 22:32.310
He has a brother who died because of him,

22:32.310 --> 22:34.170
a mother who fears him extremely,

22:34.260 --> 22:36.520
and a father his mother sees as an animal.

22:37.830 --> 22:40.160
This information is very important to us.

22:40.160 --> 22:41.760
Knowing what happened to him

22:42.270 --> 22:44.530
will make it easier to find his weakness.

22:46.030 --> 22:47.200
Anyway,

22:47.860 --> 22:49.380
this trip to Huaiguang

22:49.920 --> 22:51.980
still yielded a major breakthrough.

22:53.880 --> 22:55.520
But I really didn't imagine

22:55.620 --> 22:57.680
Qi Zhen could live such a normal life.

22:57.900 --> 22:59.210
With Qi Yan's abilities,

22:59.210 --> 23:01.310
it would be very easy
for him to find Qi Zhen.

23:01.310 --> 23:02.770
But he neither hurt Qi Zhen

23:03.070 --> 23:04.390
nor Chief Jian.

23:04.790 --> 23:05.880
Instead, he hurt

23:06.030 --> 23:07.160
unrelated people.

23:07.750 --> 23:09.070
Maybe it's because

23:10.790 --> 23:13.520
he couldn't bring himself
to hurt his own mother,

23:15.900 --> 23:16.880
so he needed to find

23:16.880 --> 23:17.790
substitutes.

23:18.030 --> 23:19.680
The women he killed

23:20.920 --> 23:22.180
were the substitutes.

23:23.880 --> 23:24.640
Yao Weihai,

23:25.480 --> 23:26.200
Cangfeng,

23:27.720 --> 23:28.780
and your brother—

23:29.400 --> 23:30.930
they were all substitutes.

23:37.110 --> 23:39.710
And I don't think
Qi Zhen lived a peaceful life.

23:39.820 --> 23:41.070
Irritability

23:41.260 --> 23:43.390
is a typical symptom of neurasthenia.

23:43.520 --> 23:45.270
She must have been in a state of tension

23:45.270 --> 23:46.750
and high pressure for a long time.

23:46.750 --> 23:47.640
Even living

23:47.640 --> 23:49.170
with a police station chief

23:49.750 --> 23:51.880
can't completely eliminate her fear.

23:51.940 --> 23:54.140
It shows how much pressure she is under.

23:54.440 --> 23:56.120
And those killed by Qi Yan

23:56.440 --> 23:57.510
were both targets

23:57.720 --> 23:58.510
and tools.

24:00.580 --> 24:01.260
So

24:02.640 --> 24:05.300
he is using his evil deeds
to torture his mother.

24:07.480 --> 24:08.400
No wonder Qi Zhen

24:08.400 --> 24:10.200
refused to admit she was Qi Zhen.

24:10.240 --> 24:12.750
She didn't want to hear or say anything

24:13.240 --> 24:14.480
because she completely denies

24:14.480 --> 24:15.550
having this son

24:15.790 --> 24:16.550
and also the existence

24:16.550 --> 24:17.920
of this whole thing.

24:19.030 --> 24:20.630
I strangled his son to death.

24:21.550 --> 24:23.030
His son died long ago.

24:24.680 --> 24:25.750
She might have really tried

24:25.750 --> 24:26.830
to strangle Qi Yan.

24:27.490 --> 24:29.010
We analyzed early on

24:29.380 --> 24:31.550
that Qi Yan was abandoned by his mother.

24:31.550 --> 24:32.950
What kind of abandonment

24:33.410 --> 24:35.590
could be more thorough and evil
than killing your own child

24:35.590 --> 24:36.310
with your

24:36.480 --> 24:37.440
own hands?

24:45.960 --> 24:47.220
Mentor sent a message.

24:48.310 --> 24:49.170
What did he say?

24:49.730 --> 24:50.450
He said,

24:50.810 --> 24:52.440
"Don't alert Jian Liang anymore.

24:52.440 --> 24:53.300
I'll follow up.

24:53.790 --> 24:55.400
You two come back when you're done.

24:55.400 --> 24:56.350
Stay safe."

24:58.720 --> 25:01.180
The enemy is in the dark
and we are in the open.

25:04.440 --> 25:05.640
You must be careful.

25:12.160 --> 25:13.310
Put the chair here.

25:15.960 --> 25:17.290
Put the TV here. Come on.

25:17.310 --> 25:18.270
Put it here.

25:19.830 --> 25:20.720
Put the TV here.

25:21.000 --> 25:21.590
Right.

25:21.960 --> 25:23.310
Okay, put the stereo here.

25:23.310 --> 25:25.770
Right, put all the vegetables
in the fridge.

25:29.510 --> 25:31.160
Okay, put the beer here.

25:31.350 --> 25:32.310
Right.

25:33.810 --> 25:35.610
Put the microwave on that table.

25:40.000 --> 25:42.930
It looks a bit more like a home
with this arrangement.

25:56.920 --> 25:58.440
This guy is something.

25:59.400 --> 26:01.290
He just got paid and

26:02.200 --> 26:03.530
he already spent it all.

26:04.400 --> 26:05.350
What did he buy?

26:07.160 --> 26:08.620
A sports betting website?

26:10.000 --> 26:10.890
He bet on a game.

26:11.640 --> 26:13.160
Investigate this website.

26:13.160 --> 26:14.420
Keep a close eye on him.

26:14.680 --> 26:15.400
Okay.

26:34.720 --> 26:36.030
Team Blues

26:36.430 --> 26:37.740
versus Team Damien.

27:36.680 --> 27:40.880
[Team Blues] [Team Damien]

27:43.570 --> 27:44.330
Zhou Jin.

27:44.350 --> 27:45.080
You're back.

27:46.440 --> 27:47.040
Zhou Jin!

27:47.070 --> 27:48.270
We need one more person
for the martial arts friendlies.

27:48.270 --> 27:49.030
Sign up.

27:49.330 --> 27:50.240
Have you forgotten?

27:50.240 --> 27:52.000
I performed too well last year.

27:52.200 --> 27:53.860
They unilaterally banned me.

27:54.830 --> 27:55.830
Have Zhao Ping go.

27:56.680 --> 27:58.610
Are you going to look for Chief Tan?

27:59.270 --> 28:00.580
He has a cold,
so I made him some medicine.

28:00.580 --> 28:01.380
Take it to him.

28:02.790 --> 28:03.750
He has a cold?

28:04.160 --> 28:04.790
Zhou Jin.

28:05.190 --> 28:07.110
You went on a business trip
and had a honeymoon along the way—

28:07.110 --> 28:08.200
how was it?

28:08.950 --> 28:10.440
Watch your mouth.

28:10.470 --> 28:12.200
What do they have to do with you?

28:12.270 --> 28:13.270
Just do your job.

28:13.770 --> 28:15.330
I'm just curious.

28:15.620 --> 28:16.680
You are so gossipy.

28:18.180 --> 28:18.650
Oh, right.

28:18.650 --> 28:20.220
How's the investigation going?

28:20.220 --> 28:21.200
There's no progress.

28:21.200 --> 28:22.350
We're discussing a new approach.

28:22.350 --> 28:23.610
Did you find anything?

28:25.790 --> 28:27.240
Not really.

28:29.430 --> 28:30.640
Make sure he drinks it.

28:30.640 --> 28:31.440
I'm off, then.

28:34.110 --> 28:34.880
Sign up.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.830
Sign up, everyone.

28:39.030 --> 28:39.720
Dan.

28:40.720 --> 28:42.790
Count... me out.

28:43.240 --> 28:45.300
You were in the SWAT team;
what are you afraid of?

28:45.300 --> 28:46.710
That's in the past.

28:46.730 --> 28:48.350
I'm afraid I'll disgrace our team.

28:48.350 --> 28:49.270
So you mean,

28:49.510 --> 28:50.720
I should go for you? How's that?

28:50.720 --> 28:52.110
You're guilt-tripping me. Guilt-tripping!

28:52.110 --> 28:52.920
I-I'll go.

28:52.920 --> 28:54.480
I didn't touch her. I-I didn't.

28:54.480 --> 28:55.740
I wrote your name down.

28:56.510 --> 28:57.100
Sir.

28:58.030 --> 28:59.670
Dan made this medicine for you.

28:59.670 --> 29:02.200
She told me
I have to make sure you drink it all.

29:03.210 --> 29:03.810
By the way,

29:04.350 --> 29:05.680
what's the latest clue?

29:05.790 --> 29:07.640
It seems no one outside knows.

29:07.920 --> 29:09.120
It's a secret for now.

29:23.030 --> 29:25.290
Did you find out Qi Zhen's real identity?

29:25.680 --> 29:26.680
So far,

29:27.120 --> 29:28.720
there's no record of Qi Zhen.

29:29.190 --> 29:30.390
How is that possible?

29:31.310 --> 29:33.370
Chief Jian's wife is clearly Qi Zhen.

29:33.370 --> 29:35.440
After the Women's Federation saved her,

29:35.440 --> 29:37.160
she claimed she had amnesia

29:37.310 --> 29:38.590
and couldn't remember anything.

29:38.590 --> 29:40.250
Even her name was given later.

29:41.040 --> 29:44.000
We basically don't know anything
about her past,

29:44.030 --> 29:46.630
and there is no way
to track down her relatives.

29:50.310 --> 29:51.550
Then what's the clue?

29:58.270 --> 29:59.470
Look at this message.

29:59.750 --> 30:01.010
Does it mean anything?

30:06.270 --> 30:07.670
Illegal sports betting?

30:07.960 --> 30:10.760
It's a cipher for the goods trading
time and place.

30:15.350 --> 30:17.080
The afternoon of October 11th.

30:17.990 --> 30:19.270
3:4...

30:20.470 --> 30:21.620
3:40 PM.

30:22.390 --> 30:23.790
Or it could be 3:04 PM too.

30:24.750 --> 30:26.210
A place starting with "B."

30:26.680 --> 30:27.590
95...

30:27.960 --> 30:28.880
No. 95?

30:29.030 --> 30:30.000
Bus 95?

30:33.350 --> 30:34.750
Where did this come from?

30:35.000 --> 30:36.480
It's from Cangfeng.

30:36.510 --> 30:37.310
Cangfeng?

30:38.270 --> 30:39.930
Isn't Cangfeng Meng Junfeng?

30:39.960 --> 30:41.560
But Meng Junfeng already...

30:42.790 --> 30:44.310
Could you tell me

30:45.270 --> 30:46.590
who this Cangfeng is?

30:49.510 --> 30:50.720
I can only reveal

30:50.770 --> 30:52.120
a Cangfeng's identity

30:52.890 --> 30:54.470
when they are completely exposed,

30:54.470 --> 30:55.580
confirmed dead,

30:56.830 --> 30:58.090
or return victorious.

30:58.590 --> 30:59.870
After the operation begins,

30:59.870 --> 31:01.510
I will leave the phone with you.

31:01.510 --> 31:03.110
As long as Cangfeng is alive,

31:03.360 --> 31:05.070
he will definitely contact me.

31:05.070 --> 31:06.400
If the operation doesn't go well,

31:06.400 --> 31:07.200
you take over.

31:07.480 --> 31:10.010
The contact method
is in the safe in my office.

31:10.070 --> 31:10.920
The password is

31:10.920 --> 31:12.830
951018.

31:13.400 --> 31:15.080
If something happens to Cangfeng,

31:15.080 --> 31:16.750
the confidential file
will be decrypted for you,

31:16.750 --> 31:18.810
and you will naturally know who he is.

31:19.030 --> 31:20.090
This is top secret.

31:21.400 --> 31:23.200
Meng Junfeng is definitely one.

31:24.000 --> 31:24.640
But,

31:25.160 --> 31:26.420
from beginning to end,

31:27.160 --> 31:28.720
I've never asked Mr. Yao

31:29.350 --> 31:31.110
how many Cangfengs there are,

31:31.420 --> 31:33.750
and if there could be
more than one of them?

31:34.310 --> 31:35.270
Is it possible

31:35.350 --> 31:36.610
that it's Jiang Cheng?

31:39.080 --> 31:40.680
That's why I called you over.

31:42.180 --> 31:42.990
Look at this.

31:44.880 --> 31:46.810
This is a virtual overseas website

31:46.950 --> 31:48.420
set up by Mr. Yao.

31:49.560 --> 31:51.860
Cangfeng contacts him by placing bets

31:52.070 --> 31:53.270
on football matches.

32:01.080 --> 32:01.710
Map.

32:02.370 --> 32:03.170
Map?

32:17.400 --> 32:18.680
When Jiang Cheng and I were kids,

32:18.680 --> 32:20.640
we used this method to play hide-and-seek.

32:20.640 --> 32:21.680
95 bets.

32:22.160 --> 32:22.960
95.

32:23.400 --> 32:24.400
Xiali Reservoir.

32:38.870 --> 32:40.720
Mentor, what are you thinking?

32:41.920 --> 32:43.440
Tell me your thoughts.

32:46.010 --> 32:47.200
This is the only

32:47.220 --> 32:48.480
direct clue we can get.

32:48.940 --> 32:50.140
If we don't go and see,

32:50.650 --> 32:51.710
we can never be sure

32:51.730 --> 32:53.360
if our speculation is right.

32:55.320 --> 32:56.640
What is Professor Jiang

32:56.640 --> 32:57.480
busy with?

32:59.030 --> 33:00.430
He's teaching at school.

33:00.910 --> 33:02.910
Making up for the classes he missed.

33:03.380 --> 33:04.760
I would like him
to come and give some advice.

33:04.760 --> 33:05.760
What do you think?

33:06.880 --> 33:07.480
Sure.

33:08.160 --> 33:09.440
He is trustworthy.

33:10.150 --> 33:11.550
I know he is trustworthy.

33:12.200 --> 33:13.070
What I mean is—

33:13.200 --> 33:14.720
is it appropriate for him

33:16.600 --> 33:17.860
to be involved in this?

33:19.240 --> 33:21.640
Is there anything inappropriate about it?

33:22.350 --> 33:24.090
Since you,
the person involved, don't mind,

33:24.090 --> 33:25.690
I don't need to worry either.

33:25.750 --> 33:27.480
Come on, give him a call.

33:35.900 --> 33:37.400
Those who preside over a provincial-level
or higher research project

33:37.400 --> 33:39.560
and achieve great research results

33:39.750 --> 33:41.960
during the tenure
of an associate professor

33:41.960 --> 33:42.960
can become a full professor

33:42.960 --> 33:44.560
without waiting for 5 years.

33:44.990 --> 33:46.450
You should consider this.

33:46.770 --> 33:47.320
Also

33:47.350 --> 33:49.280
pay attention to your attendance.

33:52.350 --> 33:52.750
Jiang,

33:53.590 --> 33:54.750
you don't look well.

33:56.530 --> 33:57.870
I have a throbbing nerve pain.

33:57.870 --> 33:59.880
I've been sleeping too little lately.

33:59.880 --> 34:02.140
It's indeed too tiring for you
to be working for both sides.

34:02.140 --> 34:03.850
[Wife]

34:05.880 --> 34:06.880
Please excuse me.

34:07.270 --> 34:08.400
I'll head off first.

34:08.480 --> 34:08.960
Okay.

34:26.670 --> 34:27.320
Honey.

34:27.590 --> 34:29.320
It's not your wife. It's Tan.

34:32.199 --> 34:33.199
Professor Jiang.

34:34.590 --> 34:36.590
I need to bother you with something.

34:37.190 --> 34:39.030
Is something wrong with the team?

34:39.030 --> 34:41.230
See if you can take a leave and come over.

34:43.190 --> 34:44.719
I'll try to get there as soon as possible.

34:44.719 --> 34:45.080
Okay.

34:45.920 --> 34:46.520
Oh, right.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.110
I'll give you

34:48.230 --> 34:49.489
a heads-up in advance.

34:49.550 --> 34:50.400
It's about

34:50.670 --> 34:51.880
Jiang Cheng.

34:55.230 --> 34:55.630
Okay.

34:58.280 --> 34:58.880
Chief Tan.

34:59.260 --> 35:00.520
Is Zhou Jin next to you?

35:00.760 --> 35:01.550
Yes, yes.

35:02.030 --> 35:02.880
Hold on.

35:07.110 --> 35:07.920
Hansheng.

35:16.590 --> 35:18.150
Maybe he's rushing over.

35:50.610 --> 35:53.360
[Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory]

36:00.920 --> 36:03.380
Are we sure
we're only giving this tomorrow?

36:05.440 --> 36:06.990
I've already settled it with them.

36:06.990 --> 36:10.190
We'll give them a little first
for them to check the goods.

36:10.960 --> 36:12.480
Where did you agree to meet?

36:12.480 --> 36:14.010
3:30 PM at Xiali Reservoir.

36:16.630 --> 36:17.320
Remember

36:17.800 --> 36:19.060
to wear a mask and a hat.

36:19.400 --> 36:20.930
I know. And sunglasses too.

36:21.000 --> 36:22.260
It's sunny over there.

36:22.280 --> 36:24.280
I'll pick a few people to go with you.

36:24.780 --> 36:26.410
That way, if anything happens,

36:26.410 --> 36:27.610
they can help you out.

36:28.280 --> 36:29.230
There's no need.

36:29.440 --> 36:31.170
The fewer people, the simpler.

36:31.400 --> 36:32.550
Just listen to me.

36:33.470 --> 36:35.200
If you get caught by the police,

36:35.280 --> 36:36.510
we're all doomed.

36:38.230 --> 36:39.830
How are they going to help me?

36:39.860 --> 36:41.130
By shooting me dead

36:41.150 --> 36:42.680
before the police catch me?

36:44.320 --> 36:45.800
Just listen to Boss He.

36:46.440 --> 36:48.100
It's Old Scorpion's request.

36:52.510 --> 36:53.110
All right.

36:53.840 --> 36:54.450
All right.

37:18.320 --> 37:19.050
I'm not sure.

37:19.530 --> 37:20.660
Not sure about what?

37:24.710 --> 37:26.040
Let's assume he means

37:26.600 --> 37:28.060
to meet at Xiali Reservoir

37:28.170 --> 37:29.300
at 3:40 PM tomorrow.

37:30.720 --> 37:32.160
But the previous Jingang operation

37:32.160 --> 37:33.290
is a lesson learned.

37:34.140 --> 37:35.440
They first used Cangfeng

37:35.440 --> 37:37.170
to pass fake news to the police,

37:37.530 --> 37:39.130
and then lured us into a trap.

37:40.090 --> 37:42.150
I don't dare to make a hasty judgment.

37:44.240 --> 37:46.640
That's exactly what I'm worried about too.

37:47.090 --> 37:49.150
The tragedy of the Jingang operation

37:49.150 --> 37:50.550
must never happen again.

37:52.020 --> 37:52.900
Is Jiang Cheng

37:54.590 --> 37:56.550
another Cangfeng?

37:57.610 --> 37:58.490
If he is,

38:00.060 --> 38:02.490
how do we explain
the fingerprints on the gun?

38:02.490 --> 38:03.090
Also,

38:04.410 --> 38:05.850
we have no idea

38:06.240 --> 38:08.570
whether he actually established contact

38:08.640 --> 38:09.720
with Leader Yao.

38:10.790 --> 38:11.850
Taking a step back,

38:12.300 --> 38:14.460
even if he is another Cangfeng,

38:15.310 --> 38:16.570
after all these years,

38:18.750 --> 38:20.210
could there be no changes?

38:23.050 --> 38:23.840
Let me go.

38:24.970 --> 38:26.770
This is indeed Jiang Cheng's way

38:26.910 --> 38:28.710
of marking a map's coordinates.

38:29.360 --> 38:31.160
Whether he works for Leader Yao or not,

38:31.160 --> 38:32.310
there are only two possibilities.

38:32.310 --> 38:32.950
First,

38:33.200 --> 38:34.260
it's another trap.

38:34.390 --> 38:34.960
Second,

38:35.120 --> 38:36.120
he has something

38:36.560 --> 38:37.620
to tell the police.

38:39.600 --> 38:40.790
Whichever it is,

38:41.000 --> 38:41.870
if I go,

38:42.560 --> 38:44.310
at least Jiang Cheng won't kill me.

38:44.310 --> 38:45.570
Don't be so confident.

38:50.000 --> 38:50.800
Right, right.

38:50.960 --> 38:52.160
Don't be so rash.

38:52.160 --> 38:54.200
Where does your confidence come from?

38:54.200 --> 38:54.750
Anyway,

38:55.640 --> 38:56.420
we need

38:57.080 --> 38:57.910
to be careful.

38:59.750 --> 39:01.120
We can't act rashly.

39:02.640 --> 39:03.080
Right?

39:20.590 --> 39:21.260
Cheng,

39:21.960 --> 39:24.560
that guy in white
over there looks like it.

39:24.940 --> 39:26.480
Why are you staring at other people?

39:26.480 --> 39:27.830
Watch your fishing rod.

39:41.700 --> 39:42.550
Do you see him?

39:43.120 --> 39:44.050
I'm not sure yet.

39:58.770 --> 40:00.290
Well, do you recognize me?

40:00.320 --> 40:01.850
Are you trying to be a thief?

40:02.000 --> 40:03.200
I'm stalking a thief.

40:04.390 --> 40:05.600
No one can tell, right?

40:05.600 --> 40:06.390
It's perfect.

40:06.390 --> 40:07.520
Even a ghost couldn't recognize you.

40:07.520 --> 40:08.750
Then I won't call you Jin anymore.

40:08.750 --> 40:10.010
I'll call you ghostie.

40:17.420 --> 40:18.150
I can confirm

40:18.440 --> 40:19.680
this guy is Jiang Cheng.

40:19.680 --> 40:21.050
Yes, I see him.

40:25.610 --> 40:26.610
Should we go over?

40:27.540 --> 40:29.000
There are too many people.

40:29.280 --> 40:30.070
Let's wait.

40:39.490 --> 40:40.520
Did you catch all these?

40:40.520 --> 40:41.040
Yes.

40:47.630 --> 40:49.030
Are they making the deal?

40:49.140 --> 40:49.700
Yes.

40:52.580 --> 40:53.430
It's time.

40:56.920 --> 40:57.980
You're quite good.

40:58.390 --> 40:59.320
Not bad, I guess.

41:24.620 --> 41:25.620
Should we go over?

41:26.230 --> 41:26.840
Let's go.

41:28.020 --> 41:29.350
Let's go down together.

41:29.450 --> 41:31.100
You get as close to him as possible.

41:31.100 --> 41:32.770
Show up in his line of sight,

41:33.060 --> 41:34.390
but don't make contact.

41:37.350 --> 41:38.220
Wait, wait.

41:42.270 --> 41:44.470
The guy who just made the deal is coming.

41:47.350 --> 41:48.410
Should we take him?

41:48.740 --> 41:50.270
Let's not alert him for now.

41:53.170 --> 41:53.700
Let's go.

41:57.600 --> 41:58.930
Should we go?

42:00.490 --> 42:01.450
What's the rush?

42:01.880 --> 42:03.840
It's too obvious if we follow too closely.

42:03.840 --> 42:04.320
Right.

42:13.240 --> 42:15.210
Send the license plate
and car model to Bai Yang.

42:15.210 --> 42:16.410
Have him check it.

42:17.060 --> 42:17.580
Yes.
